Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,\NGloria and Excelsius Dio. All praise and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,glory be to thee, O Lord most high.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you forget to cross yourself,\Nyou're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were going to talk about\Nsomething interesting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I I don't remember what it was.\NHoney, do you know what what it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,>> No.\N>> Oh, you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're up against it, Augustus.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to uh innovate.\NLook at the beautiful flowers. Aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they lovely? Oh my goodness sakes. And\Nhere's Kleenex. Well, you can't go wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,now.\NAll right. So we do have an interesting
