Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,uh of the spiritual seeker\Nuh and those that uh I found to be most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,useful\Npragmatic is I'm a pragmatist. If it
