Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, boy. Oh, boy.\N>> We're starting out with a review. A a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,small review for people who who are\N>> Oh, we're starting out with a with a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,small review for people who have never\Nbeen here before. Will that come up on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the screen now? Yep.\N>> Oh, that's exciting. Boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Golly, I forgot what I knew already.\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh dear.\NOh, we start with a map of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\NNow, the map of consciousness is world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,famous and uh a calibrated scale of the\Nvarious levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And uh throughout the lecture, Susan and\NI will very often stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh calibrate something.\NUh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,now the way we calibrate a thing is she\Nholds out her arm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I press down and I say resist.\NAll right. Now if the thing is true her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,arm stays strong.\NIf something is false, her arm goes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,weak.\NIt's never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be wrong, but I never am.\NHumility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got more humility than anybody I\Nknow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We call this asking the arm. So we ask\Nthe arm uh many questions throughout the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,day and during the months and years that\Nhave gone by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And by using the arm, we discover things\Nthat nobody else in the world knows and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody has ever known. And uh often\Nwe're the only people on the planet that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,know it.\NIf that doesn't do something for your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ego, I don't know what.\NWell, uh I thought we'd start with one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that might be on some people's mind. Uh\Nthe world is scheduled to end. I have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,permission to ask this.\NI have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is going to end today. Resist.\NWell, we thought that the lecture might
