Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> 6 o'clock.\N>> Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I don't know if that's Eastern time or\Nnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, no. I think it was 3 o'clock. our\Ntime here. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But we thought we'd just keep track of\Nwhether the world is going to end today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or not. So\Nyou know where you parked your car and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.\NWe'll have a lecture, we'll have slides,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then after that we'll have questions and\Nanswers and a free-for-all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh now the uh slides are very uh large\Nso that they can be read easily
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from the back of the room\Nand they're also large
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can see them from right up\Nhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh golly.\NYou'll find that the uh levels of
