Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh I can ask the calibrated level of\Nanything and within seconds no more than
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind has been able to learn\Nabout a subject throughout all of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,history. That's convenient, huh?\NIt's like having a complete set of
