Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh\NGod is also very demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,disapproves. He's frightening\Nsees man is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see the emotional levels in the\Nmiddle is courage. So
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,200 and over is integrity. Below 200,\Nthe integrity diminishes until you get
