Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think people even live that\Nlong when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,55. That's a grandpa or something.\NGrandpa 55.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So an archangel is a absolute entity\Ncalibrated at 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say,\N"Dear God, I ask you for help." And
