Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.80,0:34:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiness rate of people of a higher\Nlevel of consciousness is close to 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.28,0:34:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the time.\NUhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.91,0:34:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of criminality amongst people\Nof a higher level of consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.39,0:34:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,practically zero.\NSo advancing one's level of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.32,0:34:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness\Nbenefits all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.72,0:34:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits you personally\Nbenefits your destiny when you leave the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.20,0:34:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,body and go to various realms.\NYou don't want to go to the lower realms
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at all.\NAnybody here interested in exploring the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.11,0:34:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,lower realms?\NNobody that's stupid. Eh,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.11,0:35:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I did explore the lower realms. I\Nforget what the circumstances were,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.24,0:35:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I discovered I was searching for\Ntruth and uh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.16,0:35:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to a certain level\Nand I saw that nobody really ever went
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.83,0:35:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond this level. and I decided I would\Nexplore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.44,0:35:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I began to explore the lower\Nlevels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.64,0:35:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And oh yeah, that's when I gave up being\Nan atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.40,0:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave I was a diet in the wool atheist.\NYou see? Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.92,0:35:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then I took atheism to its ultimate\Nlevel and took me took it to where it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.48,0:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,would take me and I descended in and\Nexplored the lower levels of hell. And
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.35,0:36:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the lower levels of hell are so awesome,\Nsomly, awesomely horrible that I cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.24,0:36:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,really describe them. But it had to do\Nwith eternal hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.88,0:36:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, cut off from all love,\Ncut off from God
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.56,0:36:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,forever.\NWell,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're there for a while,\Nfor what forever means begins to dawn on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.44,0:36:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you.\NAnd so I investigated Dante's levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.83,0:36:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dante must I don't know how Dante knew\Nwhat it was like in hell, but his
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,description of hell was extremely\Naccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,eternal hopelessness\Nand what eternity means begins to dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.20,0:36:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on you and cold dread takes over. And I\Nasked God, I said, "If there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.52,0:36:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God, I ask him to help me\Nnow." From the very pits of hell, I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.52,0:37:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,asked God for help.\NAnd suddenly I was struck by a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.76,0:37:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,state of joy and higher level\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.07,0:37:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when the archangel responded\Nto my prayer. And I had enough good
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,karma left uh to get out of hell. And\Nthat's why I'm here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.56,0:37:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had never come out of hell, I\Nwouldn't be here today. Uhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.80,0:37:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,having explored the universe from\Nheavenly dimensions
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.72,0:37:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,uh all the way down to the uh energy\Nlevels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.96,0:37:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So let's we'll move to the\Nnext scale. The next one
