Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.92,0:38:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh the more joyful you are the closer\Nyou are to God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as we see the consciousness level of joy\Nand lovingness is way up here. All
