Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.00,0:39:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,this gives us a general feeling for the\Nrange of the levels of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.83,0:40:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make sense to people? Does it\Ndoes it fall within a pattern of
