Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And guilt calibrates much lower than\Nwhat you think it does. Guilt calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.44,0:42:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,only at 30.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.76,0:42:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the guilt peddlers then are have a\Ndestructive influence on mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.24,0:42:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to correct your behavior is\Nnot out of guilt but out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.24,0:42:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to correct your behavior is\Nnot out of guilt, but out of love for
