Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.24,0:49:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, love is steadfast.\NIt's uplifting to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.48,0:49:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So if the doggy is laying there and I\Nsend her a shot of love, I say, "Kilty."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.48,0:49:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoop! Her tail wags. Her whole life is\Ntransformed by one shot of love. From
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.72,0:49:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,being nobody\Nto being delightful and happy in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.04,0:49:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,center of interest.\NAll right. So
